value.title: Trump Has COVID. What Could It Mean For The Economy?
value.excerpt: President Donald Trump and First Lady Melania Trump have tested positive for Covid-19, the president announced on Twitter early Friday morning. Here's what to watch out for when it comes to the economy.

value.title: No one wore a mask during Trump debate prep, Chris Christie says

value.title: Boris Johnson wishes Trump 'speedy recovery' from COVID-19
